snippet.title: Something in the Water - Gamedev Progress 8 (E1M1 Game Jam)
snippet.description:
Last day of the jam! I said I was going to share some of the third level, but I'm so behind on the sprite sheet I thought at this point I may as well save it as a surprise!

The fourth and final level is extremely rough right now. I'm going to have to either start cutting ideas or somehow avoid all distractions on Friday evening :)

Wish me luck!

Something in the Water game page: https://sean-noonan.itch.io/something-in-the-water

Want to find out more? Join the Discord: https://discord.gg/rSyQths

Web: http://noonan.design
Twitter: http://twitter.com/SeanNoonan
Tumblr: http://seannoonan.tumblr.com

#E1M1 #FPS #gamedev
